# GitHub OAuth App Client ID (optional)
# Create an OAuth App at https://github.com/settings/developers
# Set "Device Flow" to enabled.
# The Client ID is NOT a secret and is safe to commit.
#
# When set, a "Sign in with GitHub" button appears on the login page,
# allowing users to authenticate via the GitHub Device Authorization Flow.
# The resulting OAuth token is used for GitHub Models (AI scanning) and
# is stored only in the browser's localStorage.
#
# If not set, users must enter a Personal Access Token manually.
VITE_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
